description:
Volleyball match score management interface.
Rules
- number of sets to win the match: 3;
- number of points for winning the Set: 25 (with at least 2 points ahead of the opponent);
- number of points for winning the fifth Set (Tie-Break): 15 (with at least 2 points ahead of the opponent);
- maximum number of substitutions per set: 6;
- maximum number of timeouts per Set: 2.

